    "text": "Think Tank Transparency Act\n\nThis bill requires U.S. nonprofit think tanks to disclose to the Department of Justice any gifts, donations, or contributions from a foreign principal in amounts of $10,000 or greater.\u00a0 The bill also requires the think tanks to disclose contracts or agreements with foreign principals."
